title: Raw Silk Imports for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1867-1886 (2)--Original Data, 1882-1924 (3)--Original Data, 1919-1940. For July 1882-1938, Data Include Waste Raw Silk; For The Period 1867-1924, Data Is For Total Imports. Figures For September, 1922 Covers September 1-21. Figures For October, 1922, Covers September 22-October 31. Source: Monthly Summary Of Foreign Commerce
